text: David Chu may refer to: * David Chu (designer), founder of Nautica, a men's designer outerwear company * David S. C. Chu, former U.S. Under Secretary of Defense for Personnel and Readiness * David Chu (Hong Kong politician), member of the Legislative Council of Hong Kong and the National People's Congress of the People's Republic of China ==See also== * David Chiu (disambiguation)
